# Payment Process Flow

## 📌 Current Flow (AS-IS)

User → Checkout → Payment Attempt → Failure → Order Blocked → No Retry → Manual Resolution

---

## 🚀 Improved Flow (TO-BE)

User → Checkout → Payment Attempt →
→ If Success → Order Confirmed
→ If Failure →

* Check failure type
* If recoverable → Retry allowed
* If non-recoverable → Show error
  → Order released if failed

---

## 🧠 Improvement

* Reduced order blocking
* Better user experience
* Automated handling of failures
